<owl:ObjectProperty rdf:about="http://www.semanticweb.org/myontology#hasRemedy">
  <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">Links a prohibition to a remedy duty triggered by violation.</rdfs:comment>
  <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">has remedy</rdfs:label>
  <vaem:rationale>[Ontology Generation Agent] Created object property: Models violation consequences
    [Pitfall Resolution Agent] Created object property: Models violation consequences
    [Pitfall Resolution Agent] Added inverse axiom: OOPS pitfall: missing inverse relationship</vaem:rationale>
